org.apache.flink.cep.nfa

类 ComputationState<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.flink.cep.nfa.ComputationState<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - Type of the input events

    public class ComputationState<T>
extends java.lang.Object
    Helper class which encapsulates the state of the NFA computation. It points to the current state, the last taken event, its occurrence timestamp, the current version and the starting timestamp of the overall pattern.
